    public static final class SlyceSearchResponseUpdate.TagFound
extends SlyceSearchResponseUpdate<java.lang.String>
    This update object is sent via SlyceSearchTaskListener#onSlyceSearchTaskReceivedUpdate(SlyceSearchTask, TagFound) when a tag has been added to the associated SlyceSearchResponse. The SlyceSearchResponseUpdate.getValue() method will return the new tag.
